<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GoalNova | Elite Football Insights & Rising Stars</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Welcome to GoalNova! Your ultimate home for professional football tactical analysis, transfer news, and deep-dive profiles on the next generation of football wonderkids.">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0d1117;
            --text-color: #c9d1d9;
            --accent-color: #38bdf8;
            --card-bg: #161b22;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #010409;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        header p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-style: italic;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #161b22;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .welcome-box {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .posts-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .post-card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .post-card h3 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .post-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: #000000;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #010409;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>GoalNova</h1>
        <p>Where Football’s Next Generation Becomes Legendary</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Nova Stars</a>
        <a href="#">Tactical Hub</a>
        <a href="#">Legends</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome-box">
            <h2>Welcome to GoalNova!</h2>
            <p>Your premier destination for deep tactical analysis, trending football improvement training insights, and tracking the world's most talented wonderkids.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Latest Football Insights</h2>
        <div class="posts-grid">
            <!-- Article 1 -->
            <div class="post-card">
                <h3>Inside Premier League Training Methods</h3>
                <p>Discover how elite English academies build the stamina, speed, and technical masterclasses of their youngest rising stars...</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Read More</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Article 2 -->
            <div class="post-card">
                <h3>The Evolution of Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>
                <p>An in-depth look at the daily routines and scoring secrets keeping CR7 at the absolute peak of world football today...</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Read More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 GoalNova. All Rights Reserved. | Designed for Next-Gen Football Fans</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
